Here's a step-by-step Azure DevOps learning guide tailored for DevOps Engineers (3+ years experience) â€” covering both theory and hands-on with pipelines, repos, deployments, and real-world scenarios.

âœ… What is Azure DevOps?
Azure DevOps is a set of development tools and services for:

Source code management (Repos)

Continuous Integration/Delivery (Pipelines)

Work tracking (Boards)

Artifacts (packages)

Testing (Test Plans)

ðŸ§­ Azure DevOps Step-by-Step Learning Roadmap
